{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals/task-31","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Slušao sam zvuk i vežbao izgovor nosnog završetka zvuka i sloga.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals","challengeType":24,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">ing</span> je kraj nazalnog zvuka. Počinje samoglasnikom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">i</span>, proizvedenim jezikom blizu nepca i ispruženim usnama. Zatim direktno prelazi na nazalni zvuk <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ng</span>, proizveden sa zadnjim delom jezika naspram mekog nepca.</p>\n<p>Ovo čini <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ing</span> drugačijim od <span class=\"highlighted-text\">in</span>, koji se završava zvukom prednje nosne paške <span class=\"highlighted-text\">n</span>. U <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ing</span>, nosni ton rezonuje u zadnjem delu usta, dajući dublji zvuk.</p>\n<p>Kada <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ing</span> je praćeno početnim konsonantima, može formirati slogove kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">bing</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ping</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ming</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ding</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ning</span>, i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ling</span>.</p>\n<p>Pokušajte da izgovorite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ing</span> po tim slogovima, a zatim koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ding</span> u različitim tonovima kao primer.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Pinyin</th>\n<th>Herufi</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">dīng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">丁</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">dǐng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">顶</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">dìng</span></td>\n<td><span class=\"highlighted-text\">定</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-nasal-finals/task-31"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"cafe.png","characters":[{"character":"Li Hong","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_pinyin_nasal_finals.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":446.1,"finishTimestamp":468.89},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":1.8,"dialogue":{"text":"ing","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":2.94,"finishTime":3.85,"dialogue":{"text":"bing","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":5.39,"finishTime":6.36,"dialogue":{"text":"ping","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":7.86,"finishTime":8.86,"dialogue":{"text":"ming","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":10.4,"finishTime":11.32,"dialogue":{"text":"ding","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":13.06,"finishTime":14.05,"dialogue":{"text":"ning","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":16.02,"finishTime":16.87,"dialogue":{"text":"ling","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":18.5,"finishTime":19.4,"dialogue":{"text":"dīng","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Li Hong","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTi